name: Kalitta Charters II "Air Horse One" 727-224AF [N725CK] Landing at Calgary Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
Always a nice visitor at YYC! In the summer when the show jumping events in Spruce Meadows take place, this bird (affectionately known as Air Horse One) comes up from the States once or twice each summer. This one came in to take some horses back to the United States after the Masters tournament was complete. Enjoy this classic, 35-year old 727 touching down!

Thanks for watching!
